{"tid":408181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱響街冇喇喇比人屌老母，重比人挑釁叫報警","createTime":"2017-09-21T04:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T04:54:56.000Z","uid":136909,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10d277d154e1d05aef8facc6e2edf4d94c42c0cc","tid":408181,"uid":136909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:22:20.000Z","msg":"事情係禁的，我棟樓一樓係貨倉，成日都有貨出入，我地部電梯又細，分單雙數樓層，但都停一樓，啱啱好正方形3&times;3，載到九個人。今日落樓時，我地四個人，三個老人家，本身已經唔係好多位，個運輸仔響一樓禁lift，車仔上一大車貨，叫佢等下班，佢死都推入唻。重要&quot;少人老母&quot;，我家老人家好愛家人，自然會發火，佢重要挑釁我地報警。<br />\n   問題就來了，（我依加非常不滿）到底可以用咩方法解決呢&hellip;&hellip;如果報警又係咪真係有用？感謝。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef0d501401ac9af7800ad12b2105eb0aeee52ef","tid":408181,"uid":71425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:24:07.000Z","msg":"冇用，直接屌返佢老母，引佢出手打你，咁樣再報警就有用"},{"pid":"faa08a87dc8b1e771ca5d131235d7deaaa06f176","tid":408181,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:25:46.000Z","msg":"只能鬥屌"},{"pid":"ce0b38cd66a0402ea082ce4d274903dcaefd34e4","tid":408181,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:26:41.000Z","msg":"報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d14b5e65e5ff2ed7b1b09d356cd5635b395e23d","tid":408181,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:29:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac9ee78991c7329e2d708e1b30c3fc7d70a07f80","tid":408181,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:31:14.000Z","msg":"打柒佢"},{"pid":"7638a08ceb732e5a2a664c450202fb44c8ed491a","tid":408181,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:32:22.000Z","msg":"廢老咪撚出街 阻鳩住條路"},{"pid":"adf3b2db66862ca4a2763847a4989804c51e90b9","tid":408181,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci